{"tid":1201654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港中學校長會: 希望政府暫緩修訂逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-06-11T05:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T06:01:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"884b92db46d75ae9bc4b50b110aa234b4845ddeb","tid":1201654,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港中學校長會發聲明，希望政府暫緩修訂逃犯條例，避免社會對立惡化。<br />\n<br />\n香港中學校長會執委會發表題為「守護學生福祉」的聲明，表示極度關注社會因政府建議修訂逃犯條例出現的社會爭拗，及對學生身心發展的影響，校長會不贊成師生以罷課表達訴求，深盼政府暫緩立法，廣泛聆聽民意，避免社會對立惡化，同時呼籲教育同工謹守崗位，守護學生褔祉。"},{"pid":"cdd6f58fce5c36c0872e503b689507db702bcf6d","tid":1201654,"uid":69930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7sKr7V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7sKr7V.jpg&h=9f7442d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8TM3HFg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8TM3HFg.jpg&h=e18dbcc5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}